videos.description: Jordan Poole hits a big-time 3-pointer as Michigan goes up 34-13 on Villanova.
videos.headline: Poole hits 3 to extend Wolverines' lead

videos.description: Charles Matthews rises for a two-handed dunk to extend Michigan's lead over Villanova in the first half.
videos.headline: Matthews finishes monster putback dunk

videos.description: Ignas Brazdeikis drops a crazy and-1 to extend Michigan's lead to 49-17 over Villanova in the second half.
videos.headline: Brazdeikis hits crazy and-1

videos.description: After an attempted steal, players from Michigan and Villanova push each other and get into a verbal altercation.
videos.headline: Scuffle ensues between Michigan and Nova players

videos.description: David DeJulius hits a big three as Michigan goes up on Villanova 70-41.
videos.headline: DeJulius hits big 3-pointer
